The,United,States,Food,and,Drug,Administration,FDA,is,the,nation,s,regulatory,body,for,food,and,drug,products,The,administration,reviews,new,products,as,well,as,oversees,the,management,of,food,related,issues,around,the,country,The,FDA,Content,Syndication,API,uses,REST,calls,and,returns,XML,The,API,is,designed,to,allows,users,to,subscribe,to,news,feeds,on,FDA,topics,to,allow,users,to,be,alerted,when,new,content,is,added,to,a,topic